      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="4415th">4415th meeting</inline>, on<docDate date="2001-11-14" refersTo="#adoptionDate">14 November 2001</docDate></docTitle>
